In January 1998 the company Electronic Arts has released Diablo version for the PSX or PlayStation . In this article I will try to bring you what were the main differences between the version designed for PC / Mac and the version for the PSX . Unfortunately, the quality of the screenshots presented in the article is not the highest , because I did it with a PSX emulator , and Diablo is one of the few games which emulators do not do well. After all, the quality of the screenshots is not so tragic , and more than enough to see the appearance of the game . In addition, the article was accompanied by video clips recorded during the game . These files have been recorded by Dithrim'a and myself or Noktis'a :-) I think that movie Dithrim'a is faster than a normal game , and in my time frames were lost . However, this does not prevent hearing the beauty of the game.
